{
  "stem": "6130.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were there-- bodies one on the top of the other, because there were at least three times as many people-- women, only women in that Birkenau lager.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Auschwitz-Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At least three times as many as could go in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We weren't-- Oh, I didn't-- forgot to say that when we got out of the showers, we were all shaved completely.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Not only completely-- became completely bald, but even our female-- our female organs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Everything-- not one piece of hair was left on us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So while we were there, sometimes I'm, where is my sister?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I thought that was a young man lying there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You didn't recognize each other because of the baldness.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We all looked like men somehow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, we were lying there, one on the top of the other, the buttock on the other buttock.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was a horrible thing there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then say our prayers, you know, but saying our prayers hard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All the time in the scorching heat there in Auschwitz-- scorching heat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "July.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were taken there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My sister's-- my niece's birthday was July 3rd.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were going away maybe on the 5th.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'44. 1944.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So we have the zahlappells, and we've got blisters on our-- on our skulls.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Excuse me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Zahlappells is--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's counting the bodies.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, how many are there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Germans are very good at keeping things in order.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] By the time we got there, they didn't care about our names.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't get tattoos, because it was already late for them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Actually, Roosevelt could have saved all Hungarian Jews by that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
